summary: A small house near a waterfall to west-north from Helgen.
descriptionHtml:
A year (or two) ago I did a house for my game. After I deleted the game with this mod. But as I see I have other version, which was lost in my files^^
House have a small library corner, kitchen, bedroom and etc.
Location it's north-west from Helgen near waterwall (should be an icon of a town), I don't think you can miss it.Â 

This mod is replacer for other location where was burned people near small house, but all their items should be on the table near house (as I remember).

House placed on the border between two cells, so followers can do weird things like walking far distance, except do 5 steps to you. I don't know how to fix it, but in CK works all perfect. I think it's just a game bug. Thanks to Satan what it's happen not often.
author: minum
